    </div>
  </div>
</section>


<section id="how-it-works" class="px-6 lg:px-10 py-24 lg:py-32">
  <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
    <div class="reveal max-w-xl">
      <p class="font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-cobalt mb-4">The pipeline</p>
      <h2 class="font-display font-semibold text-3xl lg:text-4xl tracking-tight">Five steps. Zero manual handoffs.</h2>
      <p class="mt-4 text-ink/60 leading-relaxed">Each stage runs the moment the one before it finishes — so a candidate can apply and get a confirmed interview time without anyone on your team touching a keyboard.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-16 space-y-0">

      <div class="reveal flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-6 sm:gap-10 py-8 border-t border-mist">
        <p class="font-mono text-sm text-ink/35 sm:w-12 shrink-0">01</p>
        <div class="sm:w-56 shrink-0">
          <p class="font-display font-medium text-lg">Post once, everywhere</p>
        </div>
        <p class="text-ink/60 leading-relaxed">Create a role inside Hireflow and it's published straight to LinkedIn — same description, same screening questions, no second tab.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="reveal flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-6 sm:gap-10 py-8 border-t border-mist">
        <p class="font-mono text-sm text-ink/35 sm:w-12 shrink-0">02</p>
        <div class="sm:w-56 shrink-0">
          <p class="font-display font-medium text-lg">Resumes land where you already work</p>
        </div>
        <p class="text-ink/60 leading-relaxed">Applications arrive by email, the way candidates expect. Hireflow watches the inbox so no one has to refresh it.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="reveal flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-6 sm:gap-10 py-8 border-t border-mist">
        <p class="font-mono text-sm text-ink/35 sm:w-12 shrink-0">03</p>
        <div class="sm:w-56 shrink-0">
          <p class="font-display font-medium text-lg">Read in seconds, not skimmed in minutes</p>
        </div>
        <p class="text-ink/60 leading-relaxed">Skills, experience, and fit are pulled from every resume automatically and scored against the role.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="reveal flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-6 sm:gap-10 py-8 border-t border-mist">
        <p class="font-mono text-sm text-ink/35 sm:w-12 shrink-0">04</p>
        <div class="sm:w-56 shrink-0">
          <p class="font-display font-medium text-lg">Every candidate hears back</p>
        </div>
        <p class="text-ink/60 leading-relaxed">A personalized reply goes out automatically — advance, hold, or a polite no — in your company's voice.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="reveal flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-6 sm:gap-10 py-8 border-t border-b border-mist">
        <p class="font-mono text-sm text-ink/35 sm:w-12 shrink-0">05</p>
        <div class="sm:w-56 shrink-0">
          <p class="font-display font-medium text-lg">Meetings fix themselves</p>
        </div>
        <p class="text-ink/60 leading-relaxed">Shortlisted candidates get a booking link against your real availability. Confirmed slots sync straight to your calendar.</p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

